{"tid":414145,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴利獲阿仙奴贈633號波衫","createTime":"2017-09-26T03:51:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T08:15:38.000Z","uid":46892,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e0dc9271817c85188a4301566fde1bb06eff1799","tid":414145,"uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T03:51:07.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=YYUhF8%2F1gLMKNsAr01a8F%2BPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=5fbb0b6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】西布朗不敵阿仙奴，不過老將巴利刷新英超最多上陣紀錄，並獲敵方陣營送贈一件633號波衫以作留念。<br />\n<br />\n現年36歲的老將巴利（Gareth Barry）在這場比賽以正選身份出任西布朗隊長，並以英超上陣633場，打破賽前與傑斯一起保持的632場紀錄。賽後，阿仙奴領隊雲加親手送贈一件印上633號碼，以及簽滿阿仙奴球員簽名的波衫，作為對這英超長青樹的尊重。<br />\n<br />\n「這星期是有點特別，我成為很多媒體的焦點。」今仗又踢足90分鐘的巴利說。在巴利共21個英超球季的633場比賽中，有601場正選上陣，而且在2004年11月至2010年8月之間，曾經連續207場沒有提早退下火線，表現非常穩定。<br />\n<br />\n英超出場最多球員<br />\n巴利\t633場<br />\n傑斯\t632場<br />\n林柏特\t609場<br />\n占士\t572場<br />\n史必\t535場"},{"pid":"104144881d2262f897d72cc2143cbbfdd3dd771c","tid":414145,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T03:53:38.000Z","msg":"依條賤種 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed8f072b3db595e4dc8989e1588c788e01f55922","tid":414145,"uid":46892,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T03:56:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/nintchdbpict0003559858201-e1506379024961.jpg?strip=all&amp;w=960&amp;quality=100\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesun.co.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2Fnintchdbpict0003559858201-e1506379024961.jpg%3Fstrip%3Dall%26w%3D960%26quality%3D100&h=2c0b67bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同爺爺合照又多一份榮譽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1163c0f37751a60da2ccd8558d4ecec02c6877e","tid":414145,"uid":1262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T03:58:37.